<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL43">
<l>amaravō raṅka māṟum vētamōr nāṉku mōti</l>
<l>tamarkaḷiṟ ṟalaiva rāya cātiyan taṇarka ḷēlum</l>
<l>numarkaḷaip paḻippa rākil noṭippatō raḷavi lāṅkē</l>
<l>yavarkaḷtām pulaiyar pōlu maraṅkamā nakaru ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if they are [from] the Brahman caste—which is the head among His people,</l>
<l>reciting the unique six ancillary [Vedic treatises] along with the matchless four Vedas</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [they] become established [in mind]—</l>
<l>if they revile Your people, they themselves will be equal to outcastes</l>
<l>within a snap of a finger, [right] there! O You from the big city of Śrīraṅgam!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
